"U + Me = Us"  lol it was like are own little musical right Sarah...  So Murray had the best idea we should go singing to the old people which sounds really. Fun I really think this year is the time for giving. Man I have so much stuff to be grateful for and sometimes i think i take it for-granted. There's not one thing that i can think of that i need. I have everything a girl can wish for. So this year Christmas for me is all about giving to others. I think a lot of people should try it. Here we are wondering what we want for Christmas and some people would be happy just to have a piece of bread.  I think this year is going to be the best.

But then I'm starting on my fashion career which I'm so excited about. I never thought I'll find something that I like doing and that I'm actually good at. Well besides dancing.
